data.description: Property is Priced Extremely Well!!! To all buyers with a bit of research/due diligence you will see comps show a great short and long term investment opportunity.  Seller offering a 1% concession to all buyers.  The townhouse’s interior is equally captivating, showcasing lofty ceilings, modern flooring, and an abundance of natural light. The open layout effortlessly merges the living, dining, and kitchen spaces, facilitating easy entertaining while cooking. The kitchen is a culinary enthusiast’s paradise, equipped with stainless steel appliances, granite countertops, and ample room.  On the upper level, discover four generously-sized bedrooms, each radiating its own distinctive charm. However, the townhouse’s prime location might just be its crowning glory. Enjoy the convenience of city life with easy access to a plethora of dining, shopping, and entertainment venues, while also having the luxury of retreating to your tranquil haven at day’s end.
